Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.08,0:02:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A.G.140年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.21,0:02:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「驱蝠战役」后25年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球联邦与火星圈国家维甘的战争仍在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对维甘日渐扩大的势力范围
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球联邦政府
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正紧锣密鼓地准备着大规模反击战役
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.26,0:03:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特·明日野司令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才说什么 艾伦格雷亚斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新型机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿黛尔的试运行实验前些天完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性能出色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让它立即服役的呼声非常高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿黛尔是在高达AGE-1的基础上设计完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优先配备给前线部队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.98,0:03:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是在构思作战计划吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是那么滴水不漏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要找出维甘的所有藏身地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.28,0:03:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他们赶出这个宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.51,0:04:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战争 还会持续多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说战争的开端 「天使陨落」事件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恰巧是司令出生的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,40年了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦政府多次提出过议和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他们却一概拒绝！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们没有正常人的逻辑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与他们谈和是对牛弹琴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令还是认为 必须将维甘彻底剿灭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是全人类的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令拥有灵活的判断力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯独在这一点上却毫不退让
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说这始终是个谜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思是我的想法错了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得你是斯莱斯雷兹军校首席毕业生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.13,0:04:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么应该明白作为参谋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须积极理解司令官的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点不用我说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令 这次休假是和家人团聚？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.64,0:05:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这么打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆…不知道他现在怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你们是什么机动战士社团
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整天在校舍后面吱吱咔咔的烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.45,0:05:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很吵知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我们是经过学校同意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏威
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是找碴来要钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多余的零花钱不如拿出来大家分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只有旧式人工智能芯片级的智商
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:05:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想来要钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:06:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马希尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小子不想活了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以为所有人都怕你们就错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是那个亚瑟姆·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仗着自己是联邦军司令的儿子 嚣张是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.39,0:06:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你知道什么叫后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.41,0:06:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才好险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.13,0:07:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.74,0:07:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师如果没来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆早把他们打得四脚朝天了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜 学校里打架没好果子吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说 他们可能还会来报复
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候再扁一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.95,0:07:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动了动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏威！马希尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 大概是手腕的驱动控制系统还有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托啊大哥 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才是什么声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 刚才的声音好吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你们的…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗玛丽·斯通主动和我们说话！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能造出这样的东西太了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机…机动战士方面是我们的强项
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗玛丽 小心弄脏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 一股机油味 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗玛丽还是那么可爱 啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被机动战士缠身的家族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我 爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你还记着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 尤诺亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过真难得 爸爸能赶回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 上次是什么时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特现在是联邦军的司令官了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.68,0:09:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能总是放下军务陪着家人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 17岁了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉 麻烦再来一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷 吃得太多可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.09,0:09:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对 太公公太贪吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤诺亚怎么也说我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才第三盘而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是明日野家族世代相传的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日野家族世代相传…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆迟早必须继承它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时机到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久自然会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它会保护你 和你最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真羡慕 便宜都给哥哥占了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时时刻刻都要带在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 我会保管好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论发生什么 你也要保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是明日野家族继承者的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.91,0:10:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 下周有机动战士大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.42,0:10:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥他们在为卫冕做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 假期只有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就必须出门
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会给斯莱斯雷兹军校写推荐信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:10:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精英学校不好读
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:11:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就要用功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 想让我当军人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.27,0:11:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家安静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们班级又有了新成员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是杰哈特·葛雷德同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好好相处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座学校里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以走在走廊正中间的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是那个转校生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.03,0:11:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手是洛德阿布斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:11:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来教会你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这所学校的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 初来乍到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 明白了就好
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这部分和其他关键驱动没有形成联动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把转力控制程序换成先前的版本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里要换的话 其他关节也得换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,备份在哪里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的版本？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那版本也有问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特·葛雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有兴趣加入机动战士社团吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看条件差 去年还得了托尔迪亚冠军呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.71,0:13:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 已掌握进入卫星的路径
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上开始作战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.55,0:13:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手腕的动作还是没有改进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要求太高了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重写关节驱动程序吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一周后就比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想输给德鲁斯缇！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想输！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:55.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无论如何都想赢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 你这是在急什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想得冠军 被老爸的认可是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做得已经很棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…不是因为那些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.88,0:14:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想在格斗大赛上夺冠 没什么错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急避难警报
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈明明说托尔迪亚戒备森严不会有事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是居民区的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去大家都会遭殃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 妈妈的电话也打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.24,0:15:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.23,0:15:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.27,0:15:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把脚扭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家去 我和家里人联系不上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆　这边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡格斯 尤诺亚她们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心 和艾米莉一起到地下避难…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说那是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她受伤了 不能丢下不管
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.13,0:16:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔瑟 汉斯 咋样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备OK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时可以开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:17:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡格斯 这难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是菲利特制造出的最强机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的机动战士竟然在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 菲利特那小子故意藏在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护这座卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用它去…作战？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由你来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 爸爸知道会有这么一天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,0:17:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 到关键时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必须承担起保护大家的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是明日野家族的男人的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它会保护你和你最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.27,0:17:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会和爸爸那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡格斯 我决定干
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得好 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:17:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.88,0:18:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就能动？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.61,0:18:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日常维护从没有怠慢过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达的性能远远胜过菲利特当年用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 开动它的话马厩不会塌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.33,0:18:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别操心 乔瑟！汉斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AGE装置就是钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AGE装置…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.51,0:18:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来它就是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试试
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.62,0:18:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心着点 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.87,0:18:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士的基本操作我全掌握了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.31,0:18:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主监视器点亮 能量系统正常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AGE系统启动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起来！ 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是亚瑟姆在驾驶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.41,0:19:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是高达吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现目标！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行 我能行！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.12,0:19:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被干掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有上 我必须保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 看我一定干掉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 二刀流吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.02,0:20:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇静 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 镇静
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.21,0:20:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇静 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.11,0:20:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 那个机师让人感觉稚嫩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是外行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣的战斗方式
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.72,0:21:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩一台
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉了 赢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.55,0:21:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两台多拉多 就这么完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.17,0:21:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是高达的性能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.43,0:21:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这雾是？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.85,0:22:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.28,0:22:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达从视野中消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于还是开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.31,0:22:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我们的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.49,0:22:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想让你品尝到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.86,0:22:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去宝贵的人的滋味
